6 py-3 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-200 transition\">返回Dashboard</a></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 p-6 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-3\">如何使用调试工具</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-blue-700\"><li>1. <strong>连接测试</strong> - 检查Supabase基础连接是否正常</li><li>2. <strong>Dashboard模拟</strong> - 重现用户加载dashboard的过程</li><li>3. <strong>导出报告</strong> - 获取完整的诊断信息用于技术支持</li><li>4. <strong>清除缓存</strong> - 解决缓存导致的显示问题</li></ul><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm text-blue-600\">如果测试失败，请检查网络连接、浏览器控制台错误，或联系技术支持。</p></div></div></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-03f7c6bc932ce1e3.js\" async=\"\"></script></body></html><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0]);self.__next_f.push([2,null])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/f8bc7b451f599f89.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"2:I[2846,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n4:I[9107,[],\\\"ClientPageRoot\\\"]\\n5:I[1729,[\\\"762\\\",\\\"static/chunks/44530001-5f86e157ede9686f.js\\\",\\\"303\\\",\\\"static/chunks/303-b73a131c003791f2.js\\\",\\\"670\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/debug/page-a462a47ed9c4c26a.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\",1]\\n6:I[4707,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n7:I[6423,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n8:I[8003,[\\\"762\\\",\\\"static/chunks/44530001-5f86e157ede9686f.js\\\",\\\"303\\\",\\\"static/chunks/303-b73a131c003791f2.js\\\",\\\"972\\\",\\\"static/chunks/972-d572eae3505c0e7f.js\\\",\\\"185\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-c4b41f7f364a3c3d.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n9:I[2611,[\\\"762\\\",\\\"static/chunks/44530001-5f86e157ede9686f.js\\\",\\\"303\\\",\\\"static/chunks/303-b73a131c003791f2.js\\\",\\\"972\\\",\\\"static/chunks/972-d572eae3505c0e7f.js\\\",\\\"185\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-c4b41f7f364a3c3d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\nb:I[1060,[],\\\"\\\"]\\nc:[]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2\\\",null,{\\\"buildId\\\":\\\"XaJ5SoBDtTnYSLx4qzVY7\\\",\\\"assetPrefix\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlParts\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"debug\\\"],\\\"initial